            "title": "供應擔憂將中國銅價推至歷史新高 紐約市場同步上漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"供應擔憂將中國銅價推至歷史新高 紐約市場同步上漲\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SKFz.sNyGklBBGOmLtsMxQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/4a000030-e215-11f0-aee3-a5de876b532d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">供應擔憂將中國銅價推至歷史新高 紐約市場同步上漲</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
